OL,3,CThe wind down of SD TV, MW and LW
OL,4,Cservices
OL,6,GIf you are an observant Freesat
OL,7,Gviewer you may have noticed a little
OL,8,Gchange in the past few days.
OL,10,FThe SD versions of BBC channels
OL,11,Ffinally disappeared off the
OL,12,Felectronic programme guide on HD
OL,13,Fboxes ` months after they became
OL,14,Fcompletely redundant.
OL,16,FAll BBC national and regional
OL,17,Fservices have, of course, been
OL,18,Favailable in HD on satellite for
OL,19,Fabout 9 months.
