OL,3,CThe wind down of SD TV, MW and LW
OL,4,Cservices
OL,6,FThe SD signal was left on for the
OL,7,Fbenefit of those still using SD
OL,8,Fequipment but will finally be
OL,9,Fswitched off on 8th January.
OL,11,FThis is a reminder that the BBC has
OL,12,Fbeen exceptionally cautious to try to
OL,13,Fensure nobody is disadvantaged.
OL,15,FThe BBC could have shut down its SD
OL,16,Fservices months ago ` or at least
OL,17,Fremoved them from HD boxes completely.
OL,19,FWhat may look like overcaution has a
OL,20,Fvery good and entirely laudable
OL,21,Fexplanation.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/9
