OL,3,CThe wind down of SD TV, MW and LW
OL,4,Cservices
OL,6,FThe public service broadcaster cannot
OL,7,Frisk excluding the elderly, the
OL,8,Fvulnerable and the disadvantaged.
OL,10,FIt is safe to assume ITV, Channel 4
OL,11,Fand Channel 5 will turn off all
OL,12,Fduplicate SD satellite feeds of their
OL,13,Fmain channels in the near future too.
OL,14,FMore ITV 1 SD regions shut in January.
OL,16,FIf the departure of BBC services goes
OL,17,Fsmoothly, as will almost certainly be
OL,18,Fthe case, commercial channels
OL,19,Fcertainly should not hold back.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/9
