OL,3,CThe wind down of SD TV, MW and LW
OL,4,Cservices
OL,6,FThe moral of the story is that those
OL,7,Fwho predict the imminent end of
OL,8,Flinear television are yet again
OL,9,Fdemonstrating that they do not
OL,10,Funderstand that universal access is a
OL,11,Fvital principle of public service
OL,12,Fbroadcasting.
OL,14,FFor most of us, the red button text
OL,15,Fservice may simply seem like a
OL,16,Fnostalgic reminder of Ceefax. In
OL,17,Ffact, plans to shut it were delayed
OL,18,Fduring the early days of covid and
OL,19,Fseem to have been quietly abandoned.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/9
