OL,3,CThe wind down of SD TV, MW and LW
OL,4,Cservices
OL,6,FI am beginning to wonder if plans to
OL,7,Fmake BBC Four online only may be set
OL,8,Ffor the long grass too. This is
OL,9,Fcurrently expected in 2025 but no
OL,10,Fdate has been confirmed.
OL,12,FBBC Four is now principally an
OL,13,Farchive channel ` a place to find
OL,14,Fcontent which also appears in curated
OL,15,Fcollections and box sets on the
OL,16,FiPlayer. Yet it remains one of the
OL,17,Fmost watched digital channels at a
OL,18,Frelatively modest cost.
OL,20,FSome who do not have access to
OL,21,FiPlayer (at least on their TV) would
OL,22,Fcertainly miss it.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/9
