OL,3,CThe wind down of SD TV, MW and LW
OL,4,Cservices
OL,6,FIt is also worth noting that no date
OL,7,Fhas been announced for the closure of
OL,8,FRadio 4 Long Wave even though long
OL,9,Fwave will soon carry a full simulcast
OL,10,Fof the main FM/Digital service.
OL,12,FI suspect Radio 4 LW and 5 Live MW
OL,13,Fbroadcasts have a few more years in
OL,14,Fthem ` simply to ensure virtually
OL,15,Fnobody is left disadvantaged. They
OL,16,Fwill finally close when equipment
OL,17,Fneeds replaced or when it is possible
OL,18,Fto say with confidence that virtually
OL,19,Fnobody is listening.
