OL,3,CThe wind down of SD TV, MW and LW
OL,4,Cservices
OL,6,FAll this contrasts with what now
OL,7,Fseems to be a stampede to turn off
OL,8,Fcommercial MW radio services.
OL,10,FIt emerged over the weekend that
OL,11,FBauer is to turn off several MW
OL,12,Ftransmitters within weeks.
OL,14,FThe services affected include
OL,15,FDowntown Radio in Northern Ireland
OL,16,Fand Greatest Hits Radio in Scotland.
OL,17,FGHR's Scottish frequencies were the
OL,18,Foriginal homes of the likes of Radio
OL,19,FClyde and Radio Forth.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G7/9
