OL,3,CThe wind down of SD TV, MW and LW
OL,4,Cservices
OL,6,FThe company is acting swiftly and has
OL,7,Fclearly concluded that the negatives
OL,8,Fof an AM licence now exceed the
OL,9,Fbenefits. It will be busy encouraging
OL,10,FGHR listeners to go digital in the
OL,11,Fcoming weeks.
OL,13,FBut to expect the BBC to do the same
OL,14,Fquickly is misplaced.
OL,16,FThe public service broadcaster must
OL,17,Fbe judged by a different measure.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G8/9
