OL,3,CThe wind down of SD TV, MW and LW
OL,4,Cservices
OL,6,FLooking at its caution on SD
OL,7,Fsatellite and the Red Button text
OL,8,Fservice, it understands the need to
OL,9,Fhelp those who could easily be left
OL,10,Fbehind even if maintaining a
OL,11,Fparticular service makes no simple
OL,12,Feconomic sense.
OL,14,FAnd yet again let's say this loudly,
OL,15,Fas if we needed to. Linear BBC TV is
OL,16,Fnot going anywhere anytime soon.
